---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import DocNav from '../../../components/DocNav';
---

<Layout title="Documentation API - Authentification">
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-black text-white">
    <DocNav client:load currentPath="/docs/api/authentication" />
    
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 max-w-4xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
        Authentification API
      </h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8">
          L'API utilise l'authentification JWT avec des tokens d'accès et de rafraîchissement.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">POST /api/v1/auth/login</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">Connexion avec email et mot de passe.</p>
        
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Requête</h3>
        <div class="bg-black/50 border border-white/10 rounded-lg p-4 mb-6">
          <pre class="text-gray-300 overflow-x-auto"><code set:html={`POST /api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

&#123;
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
&#125;`}></code></pre>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Réponse (200 OK)</h3>
        <div class="bg-black/50 border border-white/10 rounded-lg p-4 mb-6">
          <pre class="text-gray-300 overflow-x-auto"><code set:html={`&#123;
  "success": true,
  "data": &#123;
    "user": &#123;
      "id": "user-id",
      "email": "user@example.com"
    &#125;,
    "accessToken": "eyJhbGci...",
    "refreshToken": "eyJhbGci..."
  &#125;
&#125;`}></code></pre>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Exemple cURL</h3>
        <div class="bg-black/50 border border-white/10 rounded-lg p-4 mb-6">
          <pre class="text-green-400 overflow-x-auto"><code>curl -X POST https://popcorn-vercel.vercel.app/api/v1/auth/login \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"email":"user@example.com","password":"password123"}'</code></pre>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">POST /api/v1/auth/register</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">Inscription d'un nouveau compte (nécessite un code d'invitation).</p>
        
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Requête</h3>
        <div class="bg-black/50 border border-white/10 rounded-lg p-4 mb-6">
          <pre class="text-gray-300 overflow-x-auto"><code set:html={`POST /api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

&#123;
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "inviteCode": "INVITE_CODE"
&#125;`}></code></pre>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Réponse (201 Created)</h3>
        <div class="bg-black/50 border border-white/10 rounded-lg p-4 mb-6">
          <pre class="text-gray-300 overflow-x-auto"><code set:html={`&#123;
  "success": true,
  "data": &#123;
    "message": "Inscription réussie",
    "userId": "user-id"
  &#125;
&#125;`}></code></pre>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">POST /api/v1/auth/refresh</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">Rafraîchir le token d'accès avec un refresh token.</p>
        
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Requête</h3>
        <div class="bg-black/50 border border-white/10 rounded-lg p-4 mb-6">
          <pre class="text-gray-300 overflow-x-auto"><code set:html={`POST /api/v1/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

&#123;
  "refreshToken": "eyJhbGci..."
&#125;`}></code></pre>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Réponse (200 OK)</h3>
        <div class="bg-black/50 border border-white/10 rounded-lg p-4 mb-6">
          <pre class="text-gray-300 overflow-x-auto"><code set:html={`&#123;
  "success": true,
  "data": &#123;
    "accessToken": "eyJhbGci...",
    "refreshToken": "eyJhbGci..."
  &#125;
&#125;`}></code></pre>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">GET /api/v1/auth/me</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">Récupérer les informations du compte connecté.</p>
        
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Requête</h3>
        <div class="bg-black/50 border border-white/10 rounded-lg p-4 mb-6">
          <pre class="text-gray-300 overflow-x-auto"><code>GET /api/v1/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN</code></pre>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Réponse (200 OK)</h3>
        <div class="bg-black/50 border border-white/10 rounded-lg p-4 mb-6">
          <pre class="text-gray-300 overflow-x-auto"><code set:html={`&#123;
  "success": true,
  "data": &#123;
    "user": &#123;
      "id": "user-id",
      "email": "user@example.com",
      "created_at": 1234567890,
      "updated_at": 1234567890
    &#125;
  &#125;
&#125;`}></code></pre>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">Utilisation des tokens</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
          Pour utiliser les endpoints protégés, incluez le token d'accès dans l'en-tête Authorization :
        </p>
        <div class="bg-black/50 border border-white/10 rounded-lg p-4 mb-6">
          <pre class="text-green-400 overflow-x-auto"><code>Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN</code></pre>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Durée de vie</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-2 mb-8">
          <li><strong>Access Token</strong> : 7 jours (configurable via JWT_EXPIRES_IN)</li>
          <li><strong>Refresh Token</strong> : 30 jours (configurable via JWT_REFRESH_EXPIRES_IN)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">Codes d'erreur</h2>
        <div class="bg-black/50 border border-white/10 rounded-lg p-4 mb-6">
          <ul class="list-none text-gray-300 space-y-2">
            <li><code class="bg-red-900/50 px-2 py-1 rounded">400</code> - ValidationError : Données invalides</li>
            <li><code class="bg-red-900/50 px-2 py-1 rounded">401</code> - InvalidCredentials : Identifiants incorrects</li>
            <li><code class="bg-red-900/50 px-2 py-1 rounded">401</code> - InvalidToken : Token invalide ou expiré</li>
            <li><code class="bg-red-900/50 px-2 py-1 rounded">400</code> - EmailAlreadyExists : Email déjà utilisé</li>
            <li><code class="bg-red-900/50 px-2 py-1 rounded">400</code> - InvalidInviteCode : Code d'invitation invalide</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>